5
00:00:34,680 --> 00:00:39,000
Recién acaba de finalizar
una reunión

6
00:00:39,120 --> 00:00:41,320
de la presidenta Cristina
Fernández de Kirchner

7
00:00:41,440 --> 00:00:44,560
